methods.addRow:
Adds a row to the table. Items will be inserted into the row the order they are put into this method

:param items: (java.lang.Object...) - The items that will appear in the row. Must be the same amount of items as columns
methods.build:
Builds the table from the TableDefinition and the rows added

:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) the table
methods.clear: Deletes all rows from the TableBuilder.
methods.rowCount:
returns the number of rows the table has

:return: (int) the size of the row List

text: Class to aid in building Tables from a TableDefinition.
